data.title: William Jennings Bryan $2 Stamp Colorano FDC Sc#2195 CO43 Great American Series
data.meta_description: This First Day Cover for the William Jennings Bryan $2 Stamp was issued in Salem, Illinois on March 19th, 1986. The cover includes a $2 stamp canceled on the First Day of Issue with a Traditional FDOI Postmark. The cachet is a beautiful "silk" design by Colorano. Thank you for your consideration.
